LIFE_OF_PI_DVS261
00:34:40,00 --> 00:34:47,50
SOMEONE stares at his son as he shoves pills into a banana. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS262
00:34:44,00 --> 00:34:49,50
SOMEONE shifts his gaze to the ship's floor. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS263
00:34:52,00 --> 00:34:56,50
Present day on a park bench. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS264
00:34:59,00 --> 00:35:06,50
The writer watches him with a furrowed brow as adult SOMEONE stares into the river before them. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS265
00:35:25,00 --> 00:35:29,50
The writer nods and grins. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS267
00:35:32,00 --> 00:35:37,50
Facing the river, he leans forward. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS268
00:35:43,00 --> 00:35:48,50
A map of the South Pacific fills the screen. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS269
00:35:51,00 --> 00:35:55,50
We zoom to the Mariana trench. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS270
00:35:57,00 --> 00:36:07,50
As we push through thick, churning storm clouds, deck lights illuminate a freighter in the night. Heavy rains pound on the swelling ocean. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS271
00:36:08,00 --> 00:36:18,50
Ramping off a wave, the ship's bow lands hard on the seething surface. Water bursts upwards as it skips to another wave. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS272
00:36:17,00 --> 00:36:23,50
Below deck, SOMEONE slowly awakes in his cabin bunk. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS273
00:36:25,00 --> 00:36:31,50
His eyes dart about. His parents sleep in a bed across the room. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS274
00:36:30,00 --> 00:36:35,50
He leans down to the bottom bunk and shakes his sleeping brother. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS275
00:36:50,00 --> 00:36:57,50
SOMEONE quickly pulls himself into his bunk as his mother rolls over. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS276
00:36:54,00 --> 00:36:59,50
The hands on a travel clock point to 1:17. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS277
00:37:01,00 --> 00:37:06,50
SOMEONE climbs a flight of stairs and enters a corridor. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS278
00:37:05,00 --> 00:37:10,50
The door swings shut behind him. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS279
00:37:07,00 --> 00:37:13,50
He staggers and steadies himself on a railing as he moves along. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS280
00:37:10,00 --> 00:37:15,50
Turning, he faces a door with a port hole. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS281
00:37:14,00 --> 00:37:19,50
SOMEONE peers through at the lightning flashing in the darkness. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS282
00:37:18,00 --> 00:37:25,50
He turns a latch and the door swings open. The wind and rain lash in at him. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS283
00:37:23,00 --> 00:37:34,50
Venturing out, SOMEONE leans over a railing and scans his tempestuous surroundings. As he steps along a walkway, his feet slide on the wet flooring. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS284
00:37:32,00 --> 00:37:38,50
He stumbles as the ship violently rocks and he catches himself on a banister. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS285
00:37:38,00 --> 00:37:45,50
SOMEONE climbs stairs to the neck deck and slides on his bare feet again. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS286
00:37:44,00 --> 00:37:51,50
He catches himself on a railing and clings to it as he beams down at the churning, roiling ocean. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS287
00:37:51,00 --> 00:37:57,50
Stepping back, he looks skyward and waves his arms giddily. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS288
00:37:58,00 --> 00:38:04,50
He struggles to perform a worshipful dance. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS292
00:38:10,00 --> 00:38:21,50
Getting to his feet, he notices a red light flashing from a high post. Falling again, SOMEONE slides into a barrier at the edge of the upper deck. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS294
00:38:20,00 --> 00:38:29,50
He braces himself and climbs to his feet. The ship plunges into a wave sending water crashing over him. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS295
00:38:26,00 --> 00:38:32,50
It leaves the upper deck flooded as he recovers. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS298
00:38:33,00 --> 00:38:40,50
SOMEONE watches two sailors moving frantically below with flashlights. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS300
00:38:41,00 --> 00:38:46,50
SOMEONE reaches for them futilely as they wash overboard. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS301
00:38:44,00 --> 00:38:49,50
Sobered, he races back inside. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS303
00:38:51,00 --> 00:38:55,50
He staggers through a corridor. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS304
00:38:56,00 --> 00:39:04,50
Finding his level flooded, he dives into the water and swims. He passes a panicking zebra. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS306
00:39:05,00 --> 00:39:08,50
SOMEONE surfaces. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS307
00:39:06,00 --> 00:39:11,50
Gasping then submerges himself and swims onward. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS308
00:39:09,00 --> 00:39:16,50
The teen passes through a dark section lit only by the pulsing red emergency lights. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS309
00:39:14,00 --> 00:39:20,50
Reaching a door at the end of the corridor, he struggles to open it. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS310
00:39:17,00 --> 00:39:24,50
It springs open releasing a powerful current of water and air bubbles. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS311
00:39:23,00 --> 00:39:31,50
SOMEONE hangs onto the door frame and tries futilely to pull himself into his family's quarters. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS312
00:39:28,00 --> 00:39:35,50
Releasing it, he drifts back down the corridor and returns to the deck. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS313
00:39:32,00 --> 00:39:36,50
An animal leaps passed him. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS315
00:39:35,00 --> 00:39:43,50
A bird seeks refuge in the nearby tower. Other animals struggle for footing on the rocking ship. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS318
00:39:52,00 --> 00:39:57,50
A sailor gives him a life jacket. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS319
00:39:56,00 --> 00:40:01,50
The Buddhist struggles to free a lifeboat carrying the cook. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS321
00:40:01,00 --> 00:40:06,50
The Buddhist leaps to SOMEONE. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS322
00:40:10,00 --> 00:40:21,50
The Buddhist, captain and the sailor shove him onto the boat. SOMEONE tumbles across the canvas cover and hangs off the edge. The cook signals to the men on the ship. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS324
00:40:20,00 --> 00:40:26,50
SOMEONE climbs back up and scrambles around as the others shout at him. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS327
00:40:31,00 --> 00:40:38,50
As SOMEONE clings to one set of lines, the cook unfastens another. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS328
00:40:35,00 --> 00:40:41,50
The Buddhist points as the zebra at the railing of an upper deck. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS331
00:40:42,00 --> 00:40:47,50
The boat tips and the cook falls off. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS333
00:40:46,00 --> 00:40:52,50
SOMEONE loses his grip on the lines and the lifeboat plummets to the sea. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS334
00:40:49,00 --> 00:41:02,50
SOMEONE lands on his belly and struggles to hold on as the boat bucks on the churning waters. SOMEONE slides backward, landing at a wave that buoys him back on the boat again. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS335
00:40:59,00 --> 00:41:07,50
It carries him past the shouting men at the edge of the ship's deck. A giant wave washes them from view. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS336
00:41:05,00 --> 00:41:13,50
The lifeboat carries SOMEONE through the wreckage. A boom sweeps low over his head. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS337
00:41:10,00 --> 00:41:27,50
Escaping the wreckage, the lifeboat briefly capsizes. As it rights itself, we find SOMEONE holding on tightly and the zebra lying inside. SOMEONE peers across the giant waves and locates the sinking ship. He notices a whistle on his life jacket and blows it. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS338
00:41:27,00 --> 00:41:32,50
He frantically waves his arm at the ship. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS340
00:41:33,00 --> 00:41:41,50
Peering into the seemingly endless expanse of rolling waves, SOMEONE spots a figure in the water. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS342
00:41:46,00 --> 00:41:58,50
Finding a life preserver, he climbs up on the canvas secured tautly over the front half of the boat. He casts the flotation device out into the water with all his might. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS343
00:41:55,00 --> 00:42:05,50
The lights of the capsizing ship twinkle and pulse in the distance as SOMEONE uses a line to reel in the drowning figure. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS345
00:42:05,00 --> 00:42:14,50
He slides a long handles oar out from beneath the canvas cover and extends it over the water toward the life preserver. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS347
00:42:13,00 --> 00:42:20,50
Two paws and a large furry head emerge from the center of the ring. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS350
00:42:25,00 --> 00:42:33,50
SOMEONE jabs futilely at the tiger with the oar. A wave carries the beast to the lifeboat's rim. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS351
00:42:30,00 --> 00:42:47,50
SOMEONE grabs on and climbs partially aboard. Scrambling to the prow, SOMEONE dives into the water. Getting his bearings, he looks back at the lifeboat, then gazes out over the roiling water. A giant wave looms stories high above him. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS352
00:42:46,00 --> 00:42:54,50
SOMEONE takes a deep breath and submerges. The wave briefly rolls him as it passes by. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS353
00:42:54,00 --> 00:43:02,50
Staying under, SOMEONE swims past a shark as he makes his way beyond the lifeboat. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS354
00:43:05,00 --> 00:43:11,50
Turning, he finds himself facing the completely submerged ship. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS355
00:43:10,00 --> 00:43:15,50
The teen halts and hovers in the water. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS356
00:43:12,00 --> 00:43:18,50
His limbs splayed as he stares at the enormous craft. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS357
00:43:15,00 --> 00:43:21,50
The deck lights glow as the ocean's depths claim the vessel. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS358
00:43:20,00 --> 00:43:26,50
SOMEONE looks on helplessly as the ship descends into the deep. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS360
00:43:26,00 --> 00:43:32,50
Turning away, he swims. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS362
00:43:38,00 --> 00:43:45,50
Two other sharks fight over a fresh kill beneath him. The tempestuous waters swirl over SOMEONE as he makes his way back to the surface. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS363
00:43:45,00 --> 00:43:50,50
The teen thrusts his head above water and gasps. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS364
00:43:52,00 --> 00:43:58,50
With long strokes, he swims back to the lifeboat. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS365
00:44:00,00 --> 00:44:09,50
SOMEONE grabs for a mast jutting five feet from the prow, but a passing wave compromises his reach. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS366
00:44:06,00 --> 00:44:11,50
Another carries him to the boat's rim. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS367
00:44:12,00 --> 00:44:20,50
SOMEONE climbs on to the deck with the zebra who lies curled up on its side on one end. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS368
00:44:17,00 --> 00:44:22,50
Knee-deep water sloshes around the deck. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS369
00:44:20,00 --> 00:44:26,50
SOMEONE climbs back on the canvas cover, then scrambles to the prow. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS370
00:44:24,00 --> 00:44:29,50
He leans far out, clinging to the mast. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS371
00:44:26,00 --> 00:44:32,50
A wave sends a blast of spray into his face. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS372
00:44:29,00 --> 00:44:36,50
Shaking his head, he catches his breath and peers down into the water. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS373
00:44:45,00 --> 00:44:50,50
Another blast of sea-spray drenches the teen. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS374
00:44:54,00 --> 00:45:01,50
He watches helplessly as the ship sinks further beneath the churning waves. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS375
00:44:58,00 --> 00:45:04,50
The ocean's rippling surface distorts SOMEONE's view of the lost vessel. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS376
00:45:02,00 --> 00:45:10,50
We drift up and away from the boy as the lifeboat carries him over the ship's watery grave. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS377
00:45:10,00 --> 00:45:17,50
A section at a time, the deck lights flicker then blink out. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS378
00:45:14,00 --> 00:45:21,50
Lightning flashes then diminishes leaving the boy alone in the darkness. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS380
00:45:22,00 --> 00:45:33,50
The next day a seemingly endless expanse of choppy waves roll beneath a low ceiling of storm clouds. The lifeboat bobs amidst the whitecaps. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS381
00:45:33,00 --> 00:45:43,50
With the life preserver looped over the prow beam, a huddled, shivering SOMEONE sits in the rain while clinging to the mast with his hands. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS382
00:45:40,00 --> 00:45:45,50
His feet brace against the front of the boat. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS383
00:45:43,00 --> 00:45:48,50
A shark passes beneath him. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS384
00:45:46,00 --> 00:45:54,50
Glancing down at it, SOMEONE struggles his way to the canvas covered bow and rolls over on top of the beam. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS385
00:45:56,00 --> 00:46:02,50
Lifting the edge of the canvas, he peers inside. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS386
00:45:59,00 --> 00:46:04,50
Water sloshes over the floor of the boat. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS387
00:46:01,00 --> 00:46:10,50
The water splashes the zebra who still lies curled up on the wooden bench-like seats rimming the far end. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS388
00:46:07,00 --> 00:46:15,50
One of its hind legs lies unnaturally straight as it drags its haunch along the bench. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS389
00:46:12,00 --> 00:46:18,50
Later, SOMEONE uses a bucket to bail water from the boat. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS390
00:46:15,00 --> 00:46:22,50
With weary, dogged motions, he scoops out one bucketful after another. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS391
00:46:20,00 --> 00:46:27,50
SOMEONE drops the bucket and collapses on the bench near the canvas cover's edge. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS392
00:46:24,00 --> 00:46:30,50
He leans back, his arms draped on the boat's rim and cover. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS393
00:46:30,00 --> 00:46:34,50
SOMEONE lifts his head. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS394
00:46:32,00 --> 00:46:37,50
A hyena emerges from the canvas shelter. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS395
00:46:35,00 --> 00:46:44,50
The hyena darts back under the canvas. As SOMEONE takes up a long handles oar and jumps to the canvas cover. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS396
00:46:41,00 --> 00:46:51,50
SOMEONE the hyena darts out. It leaps at SOMEONE clumsily and snaps at the oar. Its jaws clamp on the oars paddle. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS397
00:46:48,00 --> 00:46:54,50
SOMEONE drops the oar and retreats to the prow beam. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS398
00:46:51,00 --> 00:46:58,50
Clinging by his arms, he swings himself around so his legs dangle over the water. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS399
00:46:56,00 --> 00:47:03,50
Curling his abdominal muscles, he lifts his legs and fits them through the life preserver. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS400
00:47:01,00 --> 00:47:14,50
From his makeshift seat, he watches SOMEONE mid-boat as the hyena tries to climb up onto the canvas. The beast makes it only half way up, its hind legs staggering with the rocking of the boat. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS401
00:47:14,00 --> 00:47:20,50
The spotted hyena keeps its four paws on the canvas, staring at SOMEONE. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS402
00:47:20,00 --> 00:47:26,50
It turns its head. SOMEONE follows its gaze, peering across the surf. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS403
00:47:24,00 --> 00:47:31,50
From a cresting wave, an orangutan rises into view, perched on a floating bundle. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS404
00:47:33,00 --> 00:47:40,50
SOMEONE ducks into the canvas and the zebra stretches its neck toward the approaching ape. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS405
00:47:38,00 --> 00:47:45,50
As she draws near, we recognize her flotation device has bananas wrapped in netting. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS406
00:47:42,00 --> 00:47:48,50
SOMEONE extends an oar to her and she climbs aboard. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS407
00:47:48,00 --> 00:47:55,50
The teen gives her a weary smile then leans over the side of the boat. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS408
00:47:52,00 --> 00:47:58,50
In the water, the banana bundles float free of the netting. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS409
00:47:55,00 --> 00:48:00,50
SOMEONE gathers up the net. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS410
00:47:57,00 --> 00:48:03,50
Pulls out a stray banana and tosses it to Orange Juice. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS411
00:48:00,00 --> 00:48:08,50
The orangutan lets it bounce off her shoulder and land on the flooded floor of the boat. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS412
00:48:05,00 --> 00:48:12,50
Facing SOMEONE, she grimly works her lips and folds her long arms. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS413
00:48:09,00 --> 00:48:14,50
Frowning, the teen peers out over the sea. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS414
00:48:15,00 --> 00:48:27,50
As SOMEONE faces her with a concerned expression, the orangutan lowers her gaze and sighs. Turning her head over her shoulder, she gazes off over the water. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS415
00:48:24,00 --> 00:48:29,50
SOMEONE blinks understandingly. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS416
00:48:30,00 --> 00:48:35,50
SOMEONE settles wearily onto the canvas. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS417
00:48:35,00 --> 00:48:40,50
He gives a resigned sigh. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS418
00:48:39,00 --> 00:48:47,50
Now flies swarm around the injured zebra, a thin white foam covering its lips. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS419
00:48:47,00 --> 00:48:52,50
Standing on the canvas cover, SOMEONE turns. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS420
00:48:57,00 --> 00:49:02,50
He drops to all fours and picks up the bucket. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS421
00:49:00,00 --> 00:49:05,50
Lying on his belly, he slams it against the boat's hull. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS422
00:49:04,00 --> 00:49:10,50
The hyena emerges from beneath the canvas. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS423
00:49:07,00 --> 00:49:12,50
Rediscovering SOMEONE, it leaps at him. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS424
00:49:09,00 --> 00:49:15,50
The teen scrambles back and fends off SOMEONE with the oar. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS425
00:49:13,00 --> 00:49:17,50
The animal gnaws on its paddle. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS426
00:49:14,00 --> 00:49:28,50
Orange Juice scoots back on the bench and shrieks as SOMEONE bounds passed her and runs in circles. The hyena briefly leans over the edge the resumes its wild laps as SOMEONE stands ready with the oar. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS427
00:49:25,00 --> 00:49:32,50
SOMEONE stops at the center, his body convulsing. He vomits on the floor. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS428
00:49:32,00 --> 00:49:40,50
Licking his chops, he makes another try for SOMEONE but slumps weakly against the canvas. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS430
00:49:40,00 --> 00:49:46,50
The netting dangles from the base of the prow beam. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS431
00:49:43,00 --> 00:49:52,50
SOMEONE sits at the bow sharing a vigilant gaze with the hyena who remains back at the edge of the canvas. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS432
00:49:49,00 --> 00:49:55,50
The teen wavers wearily, his eyelids heavy. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS433
00:49:52,00 --> 00:49:57,50
Glancing over his shoulder. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS434
00:49:54,00 --> 00:50:00,50
SOMEONE bounds to the zebra and snaps at its injured hind leg. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS435
00:49:57,00 --> 00:50:02,50
The wounded animal kicks at the predator. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS436
00:50:07,00 --> 00:50:13,50
SOMEONE and Orange Juice watch helplessly as SOMEONE kills the zebra. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS438
00:50:19,00 --> 00:50:28,50
On a gently rolling current, SOMEONE sits in the makeshift seat at the boats prow, hugging the life preserver. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS439
00:50:25,00 --> 00:50:32,50
Dark circles shade his bleary eyes above his red, chapped cheeks. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS440
00:50:29,00 --> 00:50:34,50
SOMEONE's eyelids droop and he blinks himself awake. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS441
00:50:34,00 --> 00:50:38,50
The teen nods off again. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS442
00:50:35,00 --> 00:50:42,50
He falls back into the water, hanging by his knees from the life preserver. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS443
00:50:44,00 --> 00:50:49,50
Waking, he jolts up and gasps. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS444
00:50:46,00 --> 00:50:52,50
The sputtering teen manages to sit up and catch his breath. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS445
00:50:49,00 --> 00:50:56,50
A line of saliva streams from his mouth as he looks around and recovers. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS446
00:50:53,00 --> 00:50:58,50
In the boat, the zebra lies dead. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS447
00:50:56,00 --> 00:51:03,50
Orange Juice slumps against the edge of the canvas cover taking slow, deep breaths. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS448
00:51:10,00 --> 00:51:22,50
He lifts away a hatch beneath the canvas cover and finds a duffle inside. Opening it, he finds a red booklet titled, "Survival at Sea" lying atop an array of supplies. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS449
00:51:20,00 --> 00:51:26,50
SOMEONE takes it out and flips through pages illustrated with diagrams. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS450
00:51:24,00 --> 00:51:33,50
Lifting another hatch, the teen finds it packed with life jackets. He takes one out and tosses it to Orange Juice. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS451
00:51:34,00 --> 00:51:40,50
The orangutan picks it up, turning it in her hands and feet as she examines it. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS452
00:51:38,00 --> 00:51:44,50
Beyond her, SOMEONE digs out several more life jackets. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS453
00:51:41,00 --> 00:51:47,50
Orange Juice gives hers a shake, the throws it down. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS454
00:51:46,00 --> 00:51:54,50
Later, using ropes and netting, he bundles the life jackets together into a small, makeshift raft. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS455
00:51:51,00 --> 00:51:58,50
The life preserver crowns it and three long handled oars criss-cross out from it. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS456
00:51:55,00 --> 00:52:00,50
Forming six branch-like spokes. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS457
00:51:58,00 --> 00:52:03,50
As SOMEONE struggles to maneuver it into the water, 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS458
00:52:00,00 --> 00:52:05,50
SOMEONE emerges from the canvas shelter. 

