01:31:06,00 --> 01:31:13,50
Sunlight shines on SOMEONE who stands atop the canvas covering the lifeboat. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS908
01:31:11,00 --> 01:31:18,50
A short length of rainbow prism light filters from the dark clouds on the horizon. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS910
01:31:18,00 --> 01:31:28,50
