SOMEONE lifts his companion's head without resistance, 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS936
01:33:08,00 --> 01:33:13,50
and nestles close to the animal. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS937
01:33:10,00 --> 01:33:16,50
He rests the tigers head on his lap and softly rubs its crown. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS938
01:33:14,00 --> 01:33:18,50
He stares for a moment. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS939
01:33:15,00 --> 01:33:21,50
