LIFE_OF_PI_DVS940
01:33:21,00 --> 01:33:26,50
A teardrop travels down his face and neck. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS941
01:33:34,00 --> 01:33:40,50
Drops of rain land on SOMEONE's sun-blistered face and chest. 

LIFE_OF_PI_DVS942
01:33:37,00 --> 01:33:42,50
